{"type":"article_comment","id":226167,"parentType":"article","parentId":13651,"uid":9063,"contents":"在下愚见，对应的经文并非出埃及记，而是启示录18章巴比伦陷落。我觉得是整章对应。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31086\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\n</a>此后，我看见一个掌握大权的天使从天而降，他荣耀的光辉照亮了大地。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31087\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2&nbsp;</a>他用强而有力的声音呼喊：“陷落了！大巴比伦陷落了！<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/482\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>她成了邪灵的住处，成了所有不洁的灵体<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/92\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>和所有不洁可憎的飞鸟潜伏的地方！<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/483\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a> <a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31088\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">3&nbsp;</a>她淫乱<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>的催情酒使所有国族都沉沦了<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/484\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，地上的列王都跟她淫乱<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/485\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。她奢华无度，地上的商人<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/94\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>都因此发了财。”<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31089\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">4&nbsp;</a>我听见天上发出另一个声音，说：“我的子民啊，你们要是不想分担她的罪，不想跟她一起遭受灾祸，就要从她里面出来！<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/486\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a> <a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31090\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">5&nbsp;</a>她罪恶滔天<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/487\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，上帝已经想起她邪恶的行径<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/95\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>了<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/488\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31091\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">6&nbsp;</a>她怎样对待别人，就要受到怎样的对待<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/489\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，还要按照自己的所作所为受到加倍的惩罚<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/490\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。要在她调酒的杯里<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/491\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，调双倍的酒给她喝<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/492\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31092\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">7&nbsp;</a>她曾经有多自大、有多奢华，将来就有多痛苦、有多哀伤。她心里常常说：‘我坐在女王的宝座上，我不是寡妇，永远不会经历哀伤<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/493\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。’<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31093\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">8&nbsp;</a>因此，她的灾祸会在一天之内来到，就是死亡、哀痛和饥荒，她还要被火完全烧掉<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/494\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，因为审判她的耶和华<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/96\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>上帝力量强大<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/495\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31094\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">9&nbsp;</a>“地上的列王曾经跟她淫乱<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/97\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>，跟她一起过着奢华无度的生活，现在看见她被焚烧时冒出的烟，就都为她哭泣，悲伤捶胸。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31095\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">10&nbsp;</a>他们见她受折磨都很害怕，远远地站着说：‘这座大城<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/496\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>太惨了，太惨了！巴比伦你这座坚固的城啊，顷刻之间<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/98\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>，你就受到惩罚了！’<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31096\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">11&nbsp;</a>“地上的商人也为她哭泣哀痛，因为再也没有人买他们各式各样的货物了。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31097\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">12&nbsp;</a>这些货物包括金子、银子、宝石、珍珠、上等细麻布、紫色布、丝绸、鲜红色布、各种香木制品、各种象牙制品，还有用贵重木材、铜、铁、大理石制成的各种物品，<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31098\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">13&nbsp;</a>还有肉桂、印度香料、香、馨香油、乳香、葡萄酒、橄榄油、上等面粉、小麦、牛羊、马匹、马车、奴隶、人口。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31099\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">14&nbsp;</a>你喜爱的好东西<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/99\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>都被夺走了，你那里一切精美华丽的东西都已经消失，再也找不到了。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31100\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">15&nbsp;</a>“贩卖这些东西、靠她发财的商人见她受折磨，就很害怕，远远地站着，哭泣哀痛，<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31101\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">16&nbsp;</a>说：‘这座大城太惨了，太惨了！她一向穿着上等细麻、紫色和鲜红色的衣服，全身戴满黄金、宝石和珍珠的饰品<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/497\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31102\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">17&nbsp;</a>顷刻之间<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/100\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>，这么多的财富就被毁掉了！’<br>\n<br>\n“所有船长、坐船的人、水手，以及所有靠海谋生的人，都远远地站着，<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31103\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">18&nbsp;</a>看见她被焚烧时冒出的烟，就大喊：‘还有哪座城能跟这座大城相比呢？’<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31104\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">19&nbsp;</a>他们把尘土撒在头上，哭泣哀痛，喊着说：‘这座大城太惨了，太惨了！所有船主都是靠她发财的。顷刻之间<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/101\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>，她竟然就被摧毁了！<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/498\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>’<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31105\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">20&nbsp;</a>“高天啊，因为她的下场而欢欣吧！<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/499\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>圣民<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/500\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>、使徒、先知啊，你们也要欢欣！因为上帝已经为你们主持公道，对她作出判决了！<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/501\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>”<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31106\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">21&nbsp;</a>有一个强壮的天使举起一块磨石那样的大石头，扔进海里，说：“巴比伦大城也要这样被迅速扔下去，永远消失<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/502\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31107\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">22&nbsp;</a>你那里再也听不见弹琴唱歌、奏乐、吹笛和吹号的声音了。你那里再也找不着各行各业的工匠，再也听不见推磨的声音了。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31108\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">23&nbsp;</a>你那里再也没有灯光照耀，再也听不见新郎新娘的声音了。你的商人曾经是世上的显贵，你用通灵术<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/503\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>迷惑了所有国族。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/31109\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">24&nbsp;</a>先知、圣民和地上所有被杀害的人的血<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061170/504\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，都在这座城里找到了。”","date":"2020-02-04","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}